om New Delhi]]\n[[Category:Indian radio presenters]]\n[[Category:Indian film critics]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=October 2018}}\n{{Like resume|date=August 2016}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=October 2018}}\n\n{{Infobox person\n| name\t\t= Siddharth Kannan\n| image\t\t=\n| image_size    = \n| birth_place\t= [[New Delhi]], [[India]]\n| nationality\t= [[India]]n\n| spouse        = Neha Kannan (2 Feb 2014)\n| height\t= 6ft 2 inch (186 cms)\n| occupation\t= TV and radio host, announcer, [[voice-over]] actor, film critic<ref>{{cite news|url=http://bollyspice.com/71879/bullett-raja-gets-impressive-4-5-stars-several-top-critics|title=Bullett Raja gets an impressive 4 out of 5 stars from several top critics |date=1 December 2013|accessdate=16 April 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dhanrajfilms.co.in/reviews.html|title=Ankur Arora Murder Case Scores High on Critic Reviews|accessdate=16 April 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://twitter.com/bwooduncensored/status/426697207828324353|title=Bollywood Uncensored|accessdate=16 April 2015}}</ref>\n| years_active\t= 1994-present\n| website       ={{url|www.siddharthkannan.com}}\n}}\n\n'''Siddharth Kannan''' is an Indian television and radio host, announcer, [[voice-over]] actor and a film critic.\n\n==Early life and background==\n\nHe was born in New Delhi to parents V.Kannan and Radha Kannan, Sid K as he is popularly known as, moved to [[Kolkata]] with them and then spent 8 years in Lucknow and finally moved base with his family to Mumbai in 1994.\n\n==Career==\n\n===Radio===\n\nAt the age of 14, Siddharth joined Times FM as a Radio Host. He holds the record for becoming the youngest radio host in India.<ref>{{cite news|url= http://entertainment.gaeatimes.com/2009/05/ran03/siddharth-kannan-returns-to-his-first-love-1432/ |title= Siddharth Kannan returns to his first love|date=3 May 2009|accessdate=1 April 2015}}</ref>  In 1997, while at college, he joined Radio Star on 107.1 FM and hosted a show with Cyrus Broacha called \u2018Miranda Char Baje Band Baje\u2019. He started India\u2019s first radio school called \u2018Wild on Air\u2019 in 1999. Emirates 2 FM in Dubai syndicated their Hindi shows to him, for whom he hosted and produced shows from Mumbai.<ref>{{cite news|url= http://hamaraphotos.com/siddharth_kannan_3109.html |title=Siddharth Kannan |accessdate=1 April 2015}}</ref> He also produced and hosted shows for Rediff Radio on rediff.com. In 2009,He started an A list Bollywood  celebrity chat show \u2018Meow Starburst\u2019 on Meow 104.8fm.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/hindi/Siddharth-Kannan-on-a-roll/articleshow/45249126.cms  |title=Siddharth Kannan on a roll |date=24 Nov 2014|accessdate=1 April 2015}}</ref> Later called as \u2018Oye talkies\u2019 and then re-christened as \u2018Bollywood Khul Ke \u2018 on Oye 104.8FM(a TV Today Network initiative).<ref>{{cite news|url= http://www.afaqs.com/media/media_newslets/?id=55345_I+am+scared+of+Salman+Khan!-Karan+Johar+reveals+to+Sid+K+on+Oye+104.8+FM|title='I am scared of Salman Khan!'-Karan Johar reveals to Sid K on Oye 104.8 FM|date=29 Oct 2012|accessdate=4 April 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.indiainfoline.com/article/news-business/salman-khan-discloses-only-on-oye-104-8-fm-113110105923_1.html|title=Salman Khan discloses only on Oye 104.8 FM!|date=16 Aug 2012|accessdate=4 April 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.santabanta.com/bollywood/58867/bipasha-reveals-shes-in-love-with-brad/|title=\nBipasha reveals she's in love with 'Brad'|date=7 September 2012|accessdate=4 April 2015}}</ref> Sid K has interviewed Amitabh Bachchan,Shahrukh Khan,Salman Khan,Himesh Reshammiya,Aamir Khan,Ranbir Kapoor,Deepika Padukone and Katrina Kaif.<ref>{{cite news|url= http://www.getmovieinfo.com/pantaloons-unveil-bang-bang-collection-hrithik-roshan-katrina-kaif/07-hrithik-roshan-katrina-kaif-with-siddharth-kannan-shaking-their-legslaunch-of-bang-bang-inspired-pantaloons-collection/|title= Hrithik Roshan & Katrina Kaif with Siddharth Kannan shaking their legs@launch of Bang Bang inspired Pantaloons Collection|accessdate=1 April 2015}}</ref>\n\n=== Television ===\n\nHe hosted his first TV show in 2006 \u2013\u2019Santa and Banta Newz Unlimited\u2019 with renowned singer and rapper Baba Sehgal on Zoom.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.indiantelevision.org.in/release/y2k7/june/junerel54.php|title=Himesh Reshmmiya on the 50th episode of Santa & Banta Newz Unlimited on Zoom|date=25 June 2007|accessdate=3 April 2015}}</ref> In 2010,Sid started his next TV show \u2018See Taare Mastiii Mein\u2019 \u2013An \u2018A list\u2019 celebrity chat show on Mastiii.<ref>{{cite news|url= http://www.thaindian.com/newsportal/entertainment/siddharth-kannan-is-back-on-television_100442974.html|title=Siddharth Kannan is back on Television|date=10 Dec 2010|accessdate=4 April 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url= http://www.hamaraphotos.com/most_viewed_bollywood_photos_-_siddharth_kannan_topn_-3109_321.html |title=Salman Khan, Siddharth Kannan at IIFA Press meet to announce Chillar Film and Environment initiatives in Taj Land's End |date=5 June 2011|accessdate=1 April 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url= http://www.eventfaqs.com/ec/siddharthkannan |title= Siddharth Kannan |accessdate=1 April 2015}}</ref>  In 2012,he was the commentator on \u2018Ring Ka King\u2019 on Colors produced by Endomol India and backed by Total NonStop Action Wrestling (TNA).<ref>{{cite news|url= http://www.filmitown.com/2012/01/18/rj-cum-tv-host-siddharth-kannan-as-the-commentator-for-ring-ka-king/ |title=RJ cum TV host Siddharth Kannan as the commentator for \u2018Ring Ka King\u2019 |date=18 Jan 2012|accessdate=4 April 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url= http://tc02.tellychakkar.com/tv/tv-news/siddharth-kannan-do-commentary-ring-ka-king-go-air-28-january |title=Siddharth Kannan to do commentary in Ring Ka King; to go on air from 28 January|date=20 Jan 2012|accessdate=4 April 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url= http://www.filmyfriday.com/television/siddharth-kannan-is-back-on-television |title=Siddharth Kannan is back on Television |accessdate=1 April 2015}}</ref> In 2014,he was one of the hosts of Star Sports Pro Kabaddi and in the same year he was the host of the inaugural season of the Champions Tennis League on Sony Six.<ref>{{cite news|url= http://www.newstrackindia.com/newsdetails/2014/9/17/4-Bigg-Boss-8-Siddharth-Kannan-offered-Big-Boss.html  |title=Bigg Boss 8:Siddharth Kannan offered Big Boss|accessdate=4 April 2015}}</ref>\n<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.theindianews24.com/when-siddharth-kannan-challenged-tiger-shroff/ |title=When Siddharth Kannan Challenged Tiger Shroff |accessdate=13 February 2017}}</ref>\n\nOn 10 May 2017, Siddharth Kannan was the official [[red carpet]] host of the [[Justin Bieber]] concert at [[DY Patil Stadium]], [[Mumbai]].<ref>{{cite web|title=\nJacqueline wants to teach Justin Bieber Bollywood dance! IndiaGlitz|url=http://www.indiaglitz.com/jacqueline-fernandes-has-crush-on-justin-bieber-hindi-news-185272.html|work=IndiaGlitz|accessdate=16 May 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=\nDo you know who will host the Red Carpet for the Justin Bieber concert?|url=http://www.radioandmusic.com/entertainment/editorial/news/170510-do-you-know-who-will-host-the-red-carpet-the|work=RadioandMusic|accessdate=16 May 2017}}</ref>\n\n==Voice Overs==\nHe has been the voice over artist for the IIFA AWARDS (2000-2014), Filmfare Awards and Stardust Awards.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thehindu.com/features/metroplus/a-voice-for-all-stages/article1105498.ece |title=A voice for all stages|date=9 Feb 2011|accessdate=1 April 2015}}</ref>\n\n{| border=\"2\" cellpadding=\"4\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin: 1em 1em 1em 0; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px #aaa solid; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 90%;\"\n|- bgcolor=\"#B0C4DE\" align=\"center\"\n! Year !! Shows  \n|-\n| 2000-2004 || ''IIFA AWARDS ''  \n|-\n| 2008 || ''Ford Super Model India'' \n|-\n| 2011 || 