Kannan's b'day bash |date=31 March 2011|accessdate=1 April 2015}}</ref>  Siddharth married Neha in 2014 in Chennai and Mumbai.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.rediff.com/movies/slide-show/slide-show-1-pix-anil-kapoor-vivek-at-siddharth-kannans-wedding-reception/20140205.htm  |title=PIX: Anil Kapoor, Vivek at Siddharth Kannan's wedding reception |date=5 Feb 2014|accessdate=1 April 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url= http://timescity.com/mumbai/party-pics/siddharth-kannans-party/5745837.cms|title= Siddharth Kannan's party, Mumbai TimesCity |accessdate=1 April 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url= http://www.sify.com/movies/anil-kapoor-vivek-oberoi-and-other-stars-at-siddharth-kannan-s-wedding-imagegallery-bollywood-ocgrRAehhhcsi.html|title=Anil Kapoor, Vivek Oberoi and other stars at Siddharth Kannan's wedding |accessdate=1 April 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url= http://ibnlive.in.com/photogallery/15241.html|title=Siddharth Kannan and Neha Agarwal's star-studded wedding reception |date=5 Feb 2014|accessdate=1 April 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/events/mumbai/Siddharths-starry-wedding/articleshow/29906309.cms|title=Anil Kapoor, Sonu Sood, Shaan at Siddharth Kannan-Neha Agarwal wedding bash in Mumbai|date=6 February 2014|accessdate=31 March 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.boxofficeindia.co.in/celebs-at-siddharth-kannans-reception/|title= Siddharth Kannan|accessdate=1 April 2015}}</ref>\n\n==TV shows==\n\n{| border=\"2\" cellpadding=\"4\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin: 1em 1em 1em 0; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px #aaa solid; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 90%;\"\n|- bgcolor=\"#B0C4DE\" align=\"center\"\n! Year !! Shows  \n|-\n| 2006 || ''Santa and Banta Newz Unlimited on [[Zoom (Indian TV channel)|Zoom]]''  \n|-\n| 2008 || ''Planet Bollywood on [[Zoom (Indian TV channel)|Zoom]]'' \n|-\n| 2010 || ''See Taare Mastiii Mein on Mastiii'' \n|-\n| 2012 || ''Ring Ka King on [[Colors (TV channel)|Colors]]''  \n